SUMMER VENGEANCE MATCH UP: ROUND 2
AMI EMERSON
The Valkyrie
HT: 5'7
WT: 130lbs
Season record (2-2)
Lifetime record (2-2)
Ranked 7th
TIA LING
Jade
HT: 5'1
WT: 102lbs
Season record (1-2)
Lifetime record (1-2)
Ranked 13th
Welcome to the 2009 Championship tournament. The top 16 wrestlers of the season face off in a single elimination tournament. Check out the Summer Vengeance Bracket here.
Ami is a scrapper, a street punk, she skateboards and is generally in that group of hooligans that look like they are going to cause trouble. Competitive, strong, and determined never to lose, Ami brings intensity to every match.
Tia is one of the hottest rookies this season. She has improved ten-fold since her first match and can now hold her own. However at only 102lbs she gives up a lot to bigger girls. Tia is a fighter and never gives up for a second on the mat.
Ami was just too big and strong for our little Asian fighter. However Tia surprised Ami and made her work hard for her win. A brutal ass fucking is what happen for the loser in rd4. Ami goes on to face Vendetta in her next match up.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE TOURNAMENT MATCH UP! AMI EMERSON VS TIA LING
